    "description": "You need to go to work but you are stuck in a dream!?<br><br>No matter how much you get hurt or die, what if you are trapped in a endless dream and never wake up!?<br><br>Help the character in order to wake up!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>It consists of 8 stages, and you should control the character to reach the destination. </li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are stages you need to clear with different difficulty.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will meet lot of traps and monsters.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>So you need to find some items to escape from them.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>If you explore the map, you will be able to discover many items. </li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will need to solve some quiz.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>So you need to think a lot.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>If you're stuck on a quiz, always take a good look at the map. </li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There may be a skill that could help you with the quiz or the next stage.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Or There may be a different way to go to the next stage..</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Some 'Save Point' will make you play easy.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Acquire various skills to avoid obstacles.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230180/extras/d72da06c376c536f1a39bfeb4b140348.poster.avif?t=1680019518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230180/extras/d72da06c376c536f1a39bfeb4b140348.webm?t=1680019518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230180/extras/d72da06c376c536f1a39bfeb4b140348.mp4?t=1680019518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><